sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Sidecar as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant VLLM as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC)
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA VRAM

    Note over VLLM,GPU: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    VLLM->>S3: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>IAM / Service Account
    S3-->>VLLM: Model artifacts
    VLLM->>GPU: Load model into VRAM<br/>CUDA memory transfer

    Note over Client,VLLM: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 mTLS
    Sidecar->>VLLM: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTP/8000 localhost
    VLLM->>GPU: Run inference
    GPU-->>VLLM: Inference result
    VLLM-->>Sidecar: JSON response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON completion response

    Note over Client,TGIS: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC Generate<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033 mTLS
    Sidecar->>TGIS: gRPC GenerationService<br/>gRPC/8033 localhost
    TGIS->>VLLM: HTTP bridge<br/>HTTP/8000 localhost
    VLLM->>GPU: Run inference
    GPU-->>VLLM: Inference result
    VLLM-->>TGIS: HTTP response
    TGIS-->>Sidecar: gRPC response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: gRPC generation response
